e_France_Presse|Agence France Presse]]|via=''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]''|date=June 1, 2016|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226183338/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/01/media-groups-condemn-rodrigo-duterte-comments-journalists-philippines}}</ref>

